To use luaexpat in your lua programs you must set this environment
variable:

   LUA_INIT = "loadlib('${PREFIX}/lib/liblualxp.so','luaopen_lxp')();"

The examples have been installed in:

   ${PREFIX}/share/examples/lua

===========================================================================
